data.description: Conveniently located, this corner lot home features 1496 square feet of living space, along with a finished/attached garage, and fully fenced backyard (& side-gate for potential RV parking). The open, split-level layout features high ceilings on the entry level/main floor where the family room is located, allowing plenty of light through the large, front-facing windows. The upper level is where the open kitchen, breakfast bar, and dining area are located, featuring modern flooring with updated appliances. Just down the hall are two cozy bedrooms, as well as a full bath. On the bottom level of the home, are 2 additional bedrooms along with another full bathroom. The spacious backyard is perfect for a variety of activities including gardening, family space, or a pet play place. Home has been well maintained and is move-in ready with updated flooring, newer roof, tankless water heater, rear deck, & front steps that are all less than 2 years old. Listing Agent is also owner.
